snippet.title: Underworld Overseer - Official Release Date Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Take a look at gameplay and the world of Underworld Overseer in this trailer for the upcoming VR dungeon management game. Underworld Overseer will be available on Meta Quest and SteamVR on October 31, 2024. In Underworld Overseer, become the master of your dungeon, command your army of demons, expand your territory, place strategic traps and defeat waves of adventurers with your powerful spells.
